    h2 Overview
    p Myself along with two of my batchmates were announced as the national winners of the DesTech Challenge ‘18 organised by NASA. This article aims to explain the submission that we gave in as our entry for this challenge. For this challenge, We were required to design a digital platform to capture local urban trails through smartphones to let creatives capture, encapsulate and share their journey in a meaningful way.

    h2 About
    p DesTech Challenge is a unique national design competition in the sense that it aims to bring creative thinking and digital advancements in the built environment sector together. It challenges creative thinkers to explore opportunities within ‘Smart City’ systems, processes and engagement strategies.

    ul.single
      li.image
        img(src="../projects-destech-challenge-01.png", alt="The essence of Destech Challenge")
        span The essence of Destech Challenge
    
    p It sets itself apart from conventional design competitions by providing mentoring and research inputs from international experts to bring the best out of the participants. The challenge encourages participants to collaborate with fast-emerging digital sectors as well as local citizens to bring forward innovative ideas.

    h2 Challenge
    p Architects see the world with a creative lens. They capture their experiences through a range of mediums and build their ideas through inspirations that they come across in their environment.
    p What if they can encapsulate their experiences in a meaningful way and share it through the medium of a common platform? Imagine the possibilities generated with this exchange of thoughts to create new and innovative ideas!

