    h2 Conclusion
    p This was the first time that I participated in NASA. Since I had prior experience of designing for the digital media, my team had an upper hand in the competition and our major challenge was to come up with features that are unique and feasible at the same time. Participating in this competition not only improved my product design skills in general but also made me more knowledgable in the domain of architecture itself.